 you need an accommodationbecause of a disability, please contactthe instructor and the <ahref="http://www.disability.uci.edu/">Disability ServicesCenter</a> as soon as possible.<hr width="100%"><font face="Verdana"><font size="-1"><br><i><fontsize="-1">(C) University of California, 2008.</font></i></font></font></body></html><!--<td><ahref="other/ics221.formalSpecification.2004.ppt">Formalspecification methods</a></td>      <td class="ok">Alspaugh      <td><ahref="http://www.ics.uci.edu/%7Etaylor/ICS221/papers/e1089.pdf">[vLW98]</a>      <br><ahref="http://www.ics.uci.edu/%7Etaylor/ICS221/papers/HLK95.pdf">[HLK95]</a>      <td class="ok">Scenario analysis      <td><span class="ok">Alspaugh</span>      <td><ahref="http://springerlink.metapress.com/link.asp?id=v90uxu73cw29drka">[AP98]</a>      <br><ahref="http://doi.acm.org/10.1145/225434.225462">[Pot95]</a>-->